quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  71,11,"Alabarerera ifula ikwe nilondokhana."
  71,12,"Ne alabahelesia Omwandu nende abana, ne alabahelesia emikunda nende emialo."
  71,13,"Muli murie wamulahetsanga Nyasaye eshiriibwa tawe?"
  71,14,"Ne toto yabaloonga likhabi khwikhabi."
  71,15,"Shimulolanga shingala Nyasaye yalonga amakulu saba nikalondokhaane tawe?"
  71,16,"Ne nakhola omwesi okhubamwo obulafu, ne nakhola eliuba okhuba itaa."
  71,17,"Ne Nyasaye yabamesia khwiloba shinga emimela."
  71,18,"Khandi alibakalusiamwo, ne khandi alibarusiamwo mwesi burusia."
  71,19,"Ne Nyasaye yabakholela eshialo okhuba shinga omukeka."
  71,20,"Khomunyoole okhucheendamwo khutsinjila tsimbambalifu.’”"
  71,21,"Nuhu naboola mbu: “Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, toto bo baakhayile nibaloonda ulia owa omwandu kukwe nende omwana wuwe shibiamumetelakhwo shiosishiosi tawe halali okhusikha."
  71,22,"Ne nibakhola ebifwanga ebikhongo."
  71,23,"Ne nibaboola mbu: ‘Mlakhalekhakhwo abanyasaye benyu tawe. Ne mlakhalekhakhwo Wada, nohomba Suwa, nohomba Yaghutsa, nohomba Ya’uka nohomba Nasra tawe.’"
  71,24,"Ne toto bo bamala okhukosia abaanji, ne olametela balia abetsimbi tawe halali obukori.”"
  71,25,"Okhurulana nende tsimbi tsiabu berwa namatsi, mana nibenjisibwa mumulilo, ne shibanyoola ababahabina owulali Nyasaye tawe."
  71,26,"Ne Nuhu naboola mbu: “Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, olalekhakhwo khushialo abamenyakhwo yesiyesi mubakhayi tawe."
  71,27,"Toto Ewe nobalekhakhwo, balakosia Abasumba bobo, ne shibalebula tawe halali abonooni abakhayi po."
  71,28,"Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, ndeshela esie nende abebusi banje, nende ulia wenjila munzu yanje Omusuubili, nende balia boosi abasubila abasatsa nende abakhasi. Ne olameta abonooni shiosishiosi tawe halali okhusikha.”"